  Thread     : A lightweight sub-process; smallest unit of execution.
  Multithreading: Running multiple threads simultaneously.

  WAYS TO CREATE THREADS:
  1. Extend Thread class     -> override run()
  2. Implement Runnable      -> implement run(), pass to Thread()

  THREAD LIFE CYCLE:
